No. 10-11014. Sean Kyler, Petitioner v. Dale Artus, Superintendent, Clinton Correctional Facility. 565 U.S. 932, 132 S. Ct. 377,

181 L. Ed. 2d 238,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6386. October 3, 2011.
